    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/77c5fbed87e99c8d5615cb119888bbe3.avif?t=1757988782\" width=600 height=148 /></span>开始在<i>Starcade FACTIONS</i>中展开一段战略冒险吧——每一步都可能决定你的胜败！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/4c1fa8d65a5b6b93dcd396fd78c57552.poster.avif?t=1757988782\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/4c1fa8d65a5b6b93dcd396fd78c57552.webm?t=1757988782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/4c1fa8d65a5b6b93dcd396fd78c57552.mp4?t=1757988782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款快速的回合制策略游戏中，你不仅仅是一名指挥官，更是史诗级太空战斗的策划者。体验快节奏、充满动作的战斗，每局仅需约5分钟，非常适合快速体验高强度的游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/4aa0ade555bf79dec6c676a01965248c.poster.avif?t=1757988782\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/4aa0ade555bf79dec6c676a01965248c.webm?t=1757988782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/4aa0ade555bf79dec6c676a01965248c.mp4?t=1757988782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借战斗机、医疗兵、建造者等10种独特的舰船类型，你将发现易于上手但难以精通的多层次策略。简单的控制让任何人都能轻松上手，但只有最强者才能真正称霸。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/88146164d7709f9a18891915fd95e642.poster.avif?t=1757988782\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/88146164d7709f9a18891915fd95e642.webm?t=1757988782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/88146164d7709f9a18891915fd95e642.mp4?t=1757988782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个回合最多可进行三种强大的行动： </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 战略性地在战场上移动舰船。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 发动可能扭转战局的攻击。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 建造新舰船以增强你的力量。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务很明确：占领敌人的旗舰，在星际中赢得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/40429452becc3d86bf46c69206cad382.poster.avif?t=1757988782\" width=640 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/40429452becc3d86bf46c69206cad382.webm?t=1757988782\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/40429452becc3d86bf46c69206cad382.mp4?t=1757988782\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名独立开发者的热情之作，<i>Starcade FACTIONS</i>充满潜力。你的支持可以帮助它达到新的高度——立即免费下载并加入不断壮大的社区吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389480/extras/ebe575feb3026c883563b1e61141d3eb.avif?t=1757988782\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p>",
